  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This research is a prospective randomized controlled trial.It aimed to determine longterm
      outcomes and factors associated with increased survival after photodynamic therapy (PDT)
      through colonscopy compared with chemotherapy alone in patients presenting with advanced
      rectal cancer.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
